### TAHAP 2: JSON/API INTEGRATION

#### 2.1 Konfigurasi Equipment JSON

**Form Fields:**
| Field | Keterangan |
|-------|------------|
| API URL | URL endpoint JSON |
| Interval | polling interval dalam detik |
| Auth Type | None / Basic / Bearer |
| Auth Value | Token atau credentials |
| JSON Path | Path untuk extract data (opsional) |

#### 2.2 Logic Fetch JSON

```
javascript
async function fetchJsonData(config) {
  const options = {
    method: 'GET',
    headers: {}
  };
  
  if (config.auth === 'basic') {
    // Basic auth
  } else if (config.auth === 'bearer') {
    options.headers['Authorization'] = `Bearer ${config.authValue}`;
  }
  
  const response = await fetch(config.url, options);
  const data = await response.json();
  
  // Extract data jika ada JSON path
  if (config.jsonPath) {
    return getNestedValue(data, config.jsonPath);
  }
  
  return data;
}
```

